com.bigdata.rdf.sail.webapp.lbs.policy

Class NOPLBSPolicy

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bigdata.rdf.sail.webapp.lbs.AbstractLBSPolicy
      • com.bigdata.rdf.sail.webapp.lbs.policy.NOPLBSPolicy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    QuorumListener, IHALoadBalancerPolicy, IHAPolicyLifeCycle, Serializable

    public class NOPLBSPolicy
extends AbstractLBSPolicy
    This policy proxies all requests for update operations to the leader but forwards read requests to the local service. Thus, it DOES NOT provide a load balancing strategy, but it DOES allow update requests to be directed to any service in an non-HA aware manner. This policy can be combined with an external round-robin strategy to load balance the read-requests over the cluster.
    Author:
    Bryan Thompson
